description:
On Today's Dan Patrick, DP talks to Bengals QB Joe Burrow about their Overtime win yesterday against the Vikings. Former Browns Offensive Lineman Joe Thomas calls in to discuss what Cleveland can take away from their loss to the Chiefs yesterday. And Former QB Carson Palmer joins DP to discuss Aaron Rodgers and Matt Stafford performances in Week 1.
